LEVEL 
Classroom application

TeacherAcoustic: Teacher mote.  In its current state, the mote calibrates its acoustic sensor 
for its current environment and sends out broadcast packets instructing student motes to turn on 
green or red LED.  

StudentAcoustic: Student mote.  In its current state, the mote calibrates its acoustic sensor for its
current environment.  It will then listen for packets from the teacher mote, turning red if a red packet received
and turning green after a specified delay as contained in the packet if a green packet is received.
